# --- Live runtime data (NEVER commit user data) ---
# vault.db is the user's encrypted SQLite database. The folder may also
# hold sidecar files (-shm, -wal) and future backups. The path is
# configurable via App\appsettings.json -> Storage.DatabaseFilePath.
VaultDb/
**/vault.db
**/vault.db-shm
**/vault.db-wal

# --- Local workspace docs (kept out of source control by convention) ---
# These are scratch / planning files that live next to the repo, not
# project documentation. Add them under docs/ if they should be tracked.
/plan.md
/UI-Mockups.md
/project-instructions.md

# --- Build / tool output ---
# NOTE: /App/ is intentionally tracked — it's the deployment artifact users
# launch from. Republishing intentionally produces a diff that gets committed.
**/bin/
**/obj/

# --- Editor / OS noise ---
.vs/
.vscode/*.log
*.user
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
